title: We Call It Techno (Deluxe Version) (2018)
content: The next one is filled with sound techno, We Call It Techno a compilation giving the maximum charge and a positive mood, as well as the superiority of track saturation! With the support of performers Lasha and Lasha, Ibot, Gabbo, Brothers Dreamers, Tille Rodriguez, Jeff Leclair the contrast of this selection is filled. We believe that tracks released on BMHR will be greatly appreciated by DJs, as it will give them top notch quality tracks, that could be playable in multiple genre. Big Mamas House Records is located in the burning city Stuttgart. So they will be always ready to drop in almost any kind of set. Big Mamas House Records is committed to developing new music and artists and has a reputation for consistent excellence.
